Generic single-database configuration.
# HandsOn 7 – Alembic Migrations

## Objective

Learn database version control and schema migration using Alembic with SQLAlchemy.

## Tasks Completed

* Configured Alembic for MySQL database
* Generated and applied migrations
* Added `is_active` column to Student table
* Created `CourseSchedule` table
* Viewed migration history
* Performed migration rollback and recovery


